-- PPR Is in Exclusive Talks to Sell Conforama to Steinhoff for $1.6 Billion
-- B y   D a v i d   W h i t e h o u s e
-- 2010-12-09T06:45:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-09/ppr-is-in-exclusive-talks-to-sell-conforama-to-steinhoff-for-1-6-billion.html
PPR SA said it’s in exclusive talks
to sell its Conforama unit to Steinhoff International Holdings
Ltd. for 1.2 billion euros in cash.  PPR said in an emailed statement that shareholders with
more than 50 percent of Steinhoff’s capital have already
undertaken to vote in favor of the transaction, which PPR
expects to be concluded in coming weeks.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Whitehouse at 
 dwhitehouse1@bloomberg.net  